column16: Mookie Betts grounds into a force out, shortstop Ian Desmond to second baseman Danny Espinosa.   Brock Holt out at 2nd.    Mookie Betts to 1st.
Cesar Hernandez grounds out, second baseman Dan Uggla to first baseman Ryan Zimmerman.
Odubel Herrera pops out to shortstop Ian Desmond.
Jeff Francoeur grounds out to first baseman Ryan Zimmerman.
Craig Stammen intentionally walks Chase Utley.
Freddy Galvis strikes out swinging, catcher Wilson Ramos to first baseman Ryan Zimmerman.
Jeff Francoeur doubles (1) on a ground ball to right fielder Bryce Harper.
Darin Ruf grounds into a force out, shortstop Ian Desmond to second baseman Dan Uggla.   Freddy Galvis out at 2nd.
Chase Utley out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Michael Taylor.   Cesar Hernandez scores.
Freddy Galvis singles on a line drive to right fielder Bryce Harper.   Andres Blanco scores.    Cesar Hernandez to 3rd.    Ben Revere to 2nd.
Wilmer Flores grounds out, shortstop Ian Desmond to first baseman Ryan Zimmerman.
Travis d'Arnaud lines out to right fielder Bryce Harper.
Juan Lagares lines out to right fielder Bryce Harper.
